            <div class="title">
                Progress Of The War
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1940-03-19/debates/564a5c02-1b4b-40b9-a187-123eb5a08daa/SundayEntertainmentsAct1932" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
