<p class="">Nearly two months before that date.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-e7ff0c0a-3ba1-4f5e-a2b7-470506846daa" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
