                <div class="share-icon">&nbsp;</div><span class="share-text">Share</span>
            </a>
        </div>

    


    <div class="inner">
        <div class="col-md-9 contribution content-container">



<p class="">Then the hon. Member could not have intervened in Finland.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-79b09b14-e2f4-4fc4-a31a-417244b907a9" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
                           data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
                           data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1940-03-19/debates/bfd14d49-647a-4fb4-99e5-a29c87cbc531/ProgressOfTheWar#contribution-79b09b14-e2f4-4fc4-a31a-417244b907a9">
