            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-ee656cd4-6528-495a-895c-6e5a31ef1730">
                Mr. A. Edwards  (Middlesbrough, East)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-ee656cd4-6528-495a-895c-6e5a31ef1730" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
