                Captain Ramsay  (Midlothian and Peebles, Southern)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-f8cd375c-cb6c-4390-b84a-7dea539e08f8" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
