<p class="">They were pessimistic.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-dd5450a8-8c55-47e9-91ae-8cae1ac95e3e" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
